com.serena.dmclient.api
Class VaultObjectDetails

java.lang.Object
  com.serena.dmclient.api.VaultObjectDetails
All Implemented Interfaces:
DimensionsObjectDetails
public class VaultObjectDetails
extends java.lang.Object
implements DimensionsObjectDetails

This class contains details of a new vault object that is to be created. The only validation is upon mutually exclusive mandatory arguments that are chosen and specified via the constructors. Other than that, it is mostly just a data object to pass to the create vault object operation, for further validation and execution.
